---
title: Creamy Mustard Pork Meatball Spaghetti with Spinach & Parmesan
description: Who doesn’t love spaghetti and meatballs? Add some dijon mustard into the mixture, and toss it through a creamy, silky sauce and you’ve got a homey meal for all year round. Add some extra cheese on top to give it more of a zap.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/659b28e24a9edcff4d238be0-ddf8ddfa.jpeg
